column2: SELECT m.*, n.distance, pz.* into mydb.cUVLGs_neighbours_SDSS_#arcmin_DR1# from MyDB.cUVLGs_coordinates AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (m.RA_deg, m.DEC_deg, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON o.objid = pz.objid LEFT JOIN Photoz AS pz ON n.objid = pz.objid WHERE o.type = # and pz.photoErrorClass IN ()
